    • pizzaCostCalculator

      public static int pizzaCostCalculator​(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> toppingsList)
      ensures: returns the cost in dollars for a pizza made with the toppings found in toppingsList
      cost = $8 for zero toppings
      For greater than 0 toppings in toppingsList:
      cost = $8 + $2 each for toppings #1 and #2 and then add $1 each for toppings #3, #4, etc.
      cost = $12 for a 'special'
      a 'special' only has these 3 toppings (in any order): "pepperoni", "onions" and "sausage"
      Parameters:
      toppingsList - contains 0 or more pizza toppings
      Returns:
      the cost of a pizza based on the toppings found in toppingsList
